data.meta_description: COMPLETED DISSERTATIONS IN KIN Bound copies of doctoral dissertations conducted by KIN students can be found in the MSU Library. A list of completed dissertations follows. The student’s name is given first, then the title of the dissertation, then the advisor’s/dissertation director’s name in parentheses. Expand AllCollapse All 2020's 2023 Ault-Baker, Kylee (Ph.D.).
